data.description: Peaceful, Private, Country Home located on Almost 1 Acre at the end of the street. Front Deck overlooks spacious yard. Hardwood Floors in Living Room and Guest Bedrooms. New Laminate Floors and Large Closet in the Huge Master Bedroom. Large Kitchen with Lots of Cabinets and Counterspace. Oversized Laundry Room leads to the Back deck. All electric home also has 2 car garage and lots of storage.
